<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta name="description" content="Anonymously share your crazy experiences on OAU campus">
        <title>OAU crazy experiences</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="ui inverted segment">
            <div class="ui inverted secondary menu">
                <a href="/" id="heading" class="item">
                    <img id="logo" src="/oau.jpg" alt="logo">
                </a>
                <a href="/" class="item">
                    Home
                </a>
                <a href="/posts/new" class="item">
                    Post
                </a>
                <a href="/contact" class="active item">
                    Contact
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ui message container">
            <h2 id="info">Here you can send us a message or report a post</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="ui red message container">
            We do not support posts that goes against anonimity. If you do find
            a post exposing your identity or another person's. Kindly fill in the 
            form below and make sure you specify the id of the particular post. 
            The id is the long string being displayed beside or below the date of 
            each post. Just copy it and paste it into the post id input field. 
            Once we receive your report, we will check to see if the particular 
            post goes against our policy. It will be removed if it does. Thanks : )
        </div>

        <form method="post" action="https://formspree.io/f/mbjqeopd">
            <div class="ui form container">
                <input id="app-name" name="app-name" value="crazy-xp" type="text">
                <div class="field">
                    <div class="ui input">
                        <input name="email" type="email" placeholder="email (optional)">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <div class="ui input">
                        <input name="post id" type="text" placeholder="post id (if reporting a post)">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <div class="ui input">
                        <input name="subject" type="text" placeholder="subject (required)" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <div class="ui input">
                        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Message (required)" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <input class="ui inverted red button" name="submit" type="submit" value="Submit">
            </div>
        </form>

        <h2 id="footer">Made with ‚ù§</h2>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>